MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2017-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 2nd September, 2017
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 2nd September, 2017:
Shri Kalraj Mishra relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Micro, Small and
Medium Enterprises.
i.
Shri Bandaru Dattatreya relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Labour and Employment.
i.
Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship.
ii.
Shri Faggan Singh Kulaste relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare.
iv.
Dr. Sanjeev Kumar Balyan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Water Resources, River Development and Ganga Rejuvenation.
V.
Dr. Mahendra Nath Pandey relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Human Resource Development.
vi.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
for Cabinet Secretary

All Members of the Council of Ministers.
